6.title: Episode #1.6

6.plot: Paris Hilton enjoys an amazing jet-set lifestyle that most people can only dream about; however being on the road can get pretty lonely in and out of the spotlight. Twelve contestants (eleven girls and one boy) will compete to see if they have what it takes to be her best friend.

9.title: Episode #1.9

episode of.title: Paris Hilton's My New BFF: Dubai (TV Series 2009–2010)

9.plot: Paris Hilton must choose once and for all who is her BFF from Dubai!

imdb.plot outline: Despite having traversed the world several times over, this will be Paris's first trip to Dubai. As a result, part of the show will document her experiences on her initial voyage to Dubai. Paris will explore the desert, go camel riding, get a henna tattoo and go skiing on Dubai's famed artificial ski slope inside a shopping mall. The first episode kicks off with a social event at The BED Lounge, a premiere nightclub in Dubai. In the final episode, the final four contestants will fly to Los Angeles to see who will be crowned "Paris Hilton's BFF Dubai." PARIS HILTON'S BFF DUBAI promises to be the most dramatic, visually stunning, and most emotional BFF, yet.
